  <md:title>Forces and Torques in Muscles and Joints</md:title>
  <md:abstract><list id="list-00001">
<item>Explain the forces exerted by muscles.</item>
<item>State how a bad posture causes back strain.</item>
<item>Discuss the benefits of skeletal muscles attached close to joints.</item>
<item>Discuss various complexities in the real system of muscles, bones, and joints.</item>
</list></md:abstract>
